        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         ok, forget all this garbage, here is what you do for fastest exp.</P><P>go to DL and set up shop between ruin 2 and 3 (i think.  if you are standing on the south wall of KC and walk east down the ramp, this is the spot, not 100% sure about ruin #s)</P><P>make and haste pet, buff up, put on CoB</P><P>sow yourself, if you dont have jboots, buy sowpots otherwise this wont work as well.</P><P>run out and tag a mob with siphon str or shadow vortex, whatever you want.</P><P>run to pet, snare, fear, and dot. med</P><P>dont pull ragers or ravishers for a few more levels.  personally i never pulled ragers, they just have a ton of HPs.</P><P>when you fear the mob, he will path towards KC and along the wall, so you will NEVER get adds, unless some jackass trains one on you. If you do get an add and cant handle it, run to KC, remember, trains to the right.</P><P>you will probably never die here, if you do, you can get a rez, and you can get ports in and out of here easily. good luck.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
