        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         I am soooo old-school.  At 47 the spectres in the Feerott are giving really nice exp, so-so loot.  Over half are dark blue.  I can mash the single at the tree with maaaaybe a blue bubble of mana.  The new max-pets really mow them down.  I use an undead-only fear obviously and a dot-snare.  The dot-snare assures I get all exp.  Pet eats them.  I also pull a few from the caves.</P><P>Careful, every now and then you get one that is very resistant.</P><P>Antinice, 46th Necro, Torvus`Vir, Druzzil Ro<BR>Nothing says, "I Hate You" like a DoT<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
